title.rendered: Lip Fillers are TikTok Most Popular Cosmetic Non-Surgical Procedure

content.rendered:
With millions of people turning to TikTok for lifestyle tips and amusement, there is no denying the influence the platform has had over the years. Furthermore, with the beauty industry continuously growing, many have turned to TikTok for inspiration on the latest trends.

With that in mind, the experts at ExpressDentist.com sought to find out what the most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedures are on TikTok in 2021. By compiling a list of non-surgical cosmetic procedures, they analysed the top two viewed hashtags of each procedure on TikTok and totalled their views to discover which is the most popular overall.

Some of the highlights from the research include:

The lip filler is the most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedure on TikTok in 2021 with over 1.8 billion viewsMany people seek to have perfect brows with microblading and brow lamination being the second and third most popular procedures Lip blushing is especially popular in 2021, with this procedure having approximately 118 billion views on TikTok

THESE are the most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedures on TikTok with the number of views


It appears the influence of the Kylie lip continues to grow as ExpressDentist.com can reveal that the most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedure on TikTok in 2021 is the lip filler. This procedure has gathered a whopping 1.8 billion views on the platform from the two most popular hashtags used, #lipfiller and #lipfillercheck.


The second most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedure on TikTok in 2021 is microblading, gathering almost 1 billion views on the platform. For those who want fuller brows, microblading is a semi-permanent procedure that can help them achieve that. And although some professionals advise against this procedure, it remains extremely popular.

It seems like many people seek to have perfect brows, with the third most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedure on TikTok being brow lamination. The two most popular hashtags for brow lamination, #browlamination and #browlaminationtutorial have gathered almost half a billion views in total!


In fourth place, we find lip blushing (a semi-permanent makeup procedure meant to enhance the colour of your lips) with 118,800,000 views, followed closely by the thread lift with 118,600,000 views.

Videos of non-surgical butt procedures have been viewed 64,700,000 times, making it the sixth most popular cosmetic procedure on TikTok.

In seventh place we have the non-surgical rhinoplasty with just a little over half a billion views, this procedure consists of injecting a filler ingredient underneath your skin that will temporarily reshape your nose.

The eighth most popular non-surgical cosmetic procedure on TikTok is teeth whitening, with 46,100,000 views from people who want to find out how they can get a pearly smile.

The non-surgical face lift ranks in ninth place with 25,500,000 views, followed by jawline contouring in the last place with 15,100,000 views.

-

Methodology:

ExpressDentist.com compiled a list of non-surgical cosmetic procedures from various articles across the web. Each procedure was inputted and analysed on TikTok to discover which one has the most views on the social media platform.

As there were a large number of hashtag variations for each procedure, ExpressDentist.com selected only the first two hashtags with the most views. The first two most popular hashtags were aggregated to generate the final figure. Data was gathered on the 23rd of July 2021 and is accurate as of then.
